      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MY PICASSO (8) is an honest type in the frame at 14 of 31 starts including last time when third (30.72) over 530m at Angle Park. Goes well from this draw. Boxed wide but will go close with the right run. IZZY LETTS (5) had the drop on the lead early on but could only manage second, beaten 3 lengths (22.31) at this track in a Grade 5 over 395m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to feature again. TODD KEEPING (1) finished third (30.98) two back at Angle Park but out of the placings last time when 8th there. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. SOLO MAN (2) was well supported last time but could only manage third (22.93), beaten 4 lengths. Overdue and is among the main hopes.",
